  "title": "Part Time Pastry Assistant ($12/hour / Central / Hygiene Cert)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Japanese F&amp;B Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Salary range: $12/hour</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Flexible Working Hours</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working Location: Central</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preparing ingredients for pastry recipes.</li>\n  <li>Baking and decorating pastries, cakes, and desserts.</li>\n  <li>Maintaining cleanliness and organization in the kitchen.</li>\n  <li>Assisting with inventory management of baking supplies.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that products meet quality and presentation standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE O Level and above</li>\n  <li>1 – 3 years related experience</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
